ai_prompts.complexity_system:
You are a Home Assistant expert analysing the complexity of this {kind}.

{yaml}

Give a complexity score between 0 and 100, a one-sentence summary, and suggest a refactoring approach if score > 60. Respond in JSON: {"score": int, "summary": str, "refactoring": str|null}

ai_prompts.description_suggest_system:
As a Home Assistant expert, suggest a short description (one clear sentence, maximum 150 characters) for this configuration:

{yaml}

Respond ONLY with the suggested description, without quotes.

ai_prompts.optimizer_system:
You are a Home Assistant expert tasked with ACTIVELY OPTIMISING this automation.

{content}

Respond in JSON with the optimised YAML.
